						<div class="postbody">Well, nothing new for now...<br />I'm trying to disassemble, clean the board, check components an tracks and them will assemble again.<br />This is what I've got for now:<br /><div class="attachtitle">Attachment:</div><div class="attachcontent">
			<a href="./download/file.php?id=10464&amp;mode=view"><img src="./download/file.php?id=10464&amp;t=1" alt="IMG_2238.JPG" /></a><br />
			<span class="gensmall">IMG_2238.JPG [ 1.73 MiB | Viewed 1303 times ]</span>
		

